\c 3
\s Ukuphenduka kweNineve
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuJona ngokwesibili, lisithi:
\v 2 Sukuma, uye eNineve\x + 1.2.\x*, lowana umuzi omkhulu, utshumayele kuwo intshumayelo engikutshela yona.
\v 3 UJona wasesukuma, waya eNineve, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*. Phela iNineve\x + 1.2.\x* yayingumuzi omkhulu kakhulu, uhambo lwezinsuku ezintathu.
\v 4 UJona waseqala ukungena emzini, uhambo losuku olulodwa. Wamemeza, wathi: Kusesezinsuku ezingamatshumi amane, khona iNineve izagenqulwa.
\p
\v 5 Abantu beNineve basebekholwa kuNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 12.41; Luka 11.32.\x*, bamemezela ukuzila ukudla\x + 2 Lan. 20.3; Dan. 4.27.\x*, bagqoka amasaka\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*, kusukela komkhulu wabo kwaze kwaba komncinyane wabo\x + Jer. 6.13; Jow. 2.16.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba ilizwi lafinyelela enkosini yeNineve; yasisukuma esihlalweni sayo sobukhosi\x + Hez. 26.16; Jobe 1.20.\x*, yakhulula isembatho sayo kuyo\x + Mika 2.8.\x*, yazimbomboza ngesaka\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*\x + Isa. 58.5; Luka 10.13.\x*, yahlala emlotheni\x + Isa. 58.5; Luka 10.13.\x*\x + Jobe 2.8.\x*.
\v 7 Yasimemezela\x + Hlu. 4.13.\x* yathi kuyo iNineve ngomthetho wenkosi labakhulu bayo, isithi\x + Hlu. 4.13.\x*: Kakungabi lomuntu, kumbe inyamazana, inkomo kumbe imvu, okuzanambitha loba yini; kakungadli, kakunganathi amanzi\x + Hlab. 36.6; Jona 4.11; Jow. 1.18,20.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa kakuthi umuntu lenyamazana kwembeswe amasaka\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*, bakhale kuNkulunkulu ngamandla, yebo, baphenduke, ngulowo lalowo endleleni yakhe embi\x + Jer. 18.11; 36.3. ver. 10.\x*, lodlakeleni olusezandleni zabo\x + Isa. 59.6.\x*.
\v 9 Ngubani owaziyo, uNkulunkulu angaphenduka\x + 2 Sam. 12.22; Jona 1.6; Amos 5.15.\x*\x + Jow. 2.14.\x* azisole\x + Jow. 2.14.\x*, aphenduke asuke kukuvutha kolaka lwakhe\x + Hlab. 85.3.\x*, ukuze singabhubhi.
\p
\v 10 UNkulunkulu wasebona imisebenzi yabo, ukuthi baphendukile endleleni yabo embi\x + Jer. 18.11; 36.3; Jona 3.10.\x*\x + Jer. 18.8.\x*; uNkulunkulu wazisola ngobubi ayethe uzabenza kibo, akaze abenza\x + Jer. 18.8.\x*\x + Hlu. 2.18; Amos 7.3.\x*.
